			rendered:
				'<p>Discover the heartwarming comedy-drama Panchayat on Amazon Prime. Follow the journey of Abhishek as he takes on a job as a panchayat secretary in a small village in Uttar Pradesh. This Indian web series stands out with its fresh and unique depiction of rural life in India, balanced representation of rural life and the human experience, endearing characters and engaging storylines, making it an enjoyable escape from the mundane and perfect addition to your watchlist.</p>\n',
